Titolo: Encased: A Sci-Fi Post-Apocalyptic RPG

Anno: 2021

Descrizione: Encased: A Sci-Fi Post-Apocalyptic RPG, is an isometric turn-based RPG developed by Dark Crystal Games and inspired by games like Fallout and Wasteland as well as Soviet-era sci-fi novel Roadside Picnic. The game was released in early access on Microsoft Windows on September 26, 2019, and its full release was on September 7, 2021.